// Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-2020 — Mass File Rename (werewolves)
// Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 84eb4745-ce39-5888-a283-90cd421e4705

#event_simpleName=*
| (FilePath = *.encrypted OR FilePath = *.locked OR FilePath = *.ransom)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
